{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "vulgate:numbers.26",
    "translationId": "vulgate",
    "bookSlug": "numbers",
    "chapterNumber": 26,
    "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26",
    "summary": "Source text for Numbers 26 in Clementine Vulgate."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.1",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:1",
      "text": "Postquam noxiorum sanguis effusus est, dixit Dominus ad Moysen et Eleazarum filium Aaron sacerdotem:",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.2",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:2",
      "text": "Numerate omnem summam filiorum Israël a viginti annis et supra, per domos et cognationes suas, cunctos qui possunt ad bella procedere.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.3",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:3",
      "text": "Locuti sunt itaque Moyses et Eleazar sacerdos, in campestribus Moab super Jordanem contra Jericho, ad eos qui erant",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.4",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:4",
      "text": "a viginti annis et supra, sicut Dominus imperaverat, quorum iste est numerus.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.5",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:5",
      "text": "Ruben primogenitus Israël: hujus filius, Henoch, a quo familia Henochitarum: et Phallu, a quo familia Phalluitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.6",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:6",
      "text": "et Hesron, a quo familia Hesronitarum: et Charmi, a quo familia Charmitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.7",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:7",
      "text": "Hæ sunt familiæ de stirpe Ruben: quarum numerus inventus est quadraginta tria millia, et septingenti triginta.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.8",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:8",
      "text": "Filius Phallu, Eliab:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.9",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:9",
      "text": "hujus filii, Namuel et Dathan et Abiron: isti sunt Dathan et Abiron principes populi, qui surrexerunt contra Moysen et Aaron in seditione Core, quando adversus Dominum rebellaverunt:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.10",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:10",
      "text": "et aperiens terra os suum devoravit Core, morientibus plurimis, quando combussit ignis ducentos quinquaginta viros. Et factum est grande miraculum,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.11",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:11",
      "text": "ut, Core pereunte, filii illius non perirent.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.12",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:12",
      "text": "Filii Simeon per cognationes suas: Namuel, ab hoc familia Namuelitarum: Jamin, ab hoc familia Jaminitarum: Jachin, ab hoc familia Jachinitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.13",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:13",
      "text": "Zare, ab hoc familia Zareitarum: Saul, ab hoc familia Saulitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.14",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:14",
      "text": "Hæ sunt familiæ de stirpe Simeon, quarum omnis numerus fuit viginti duo millia ducenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.15",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:15",
      "text": "Filii Gad per cognationes suas: Sephon, ab hoc familia Sephonitarum: Aggi, ab hoc familia Aggitarum: Suni, ab hoc familia Sunitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.16",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:16",
      "text": "Ozni, ab hoc familia Oznitarum: Her, ab hoc familia Heritarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.17",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:17",
      "text": "Arod, ab hoc familia Aroditarum: Ariel, ab hoc familia Arielitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.18",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:18",
      "text": "Istæ sunt familiæ Gad, quarum omnis numerus fuit quadraginta millia quingenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.19",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:19",
      "text": "Filii Juda, Her et Onan, qui ambo mortui sunt in terra Chanaan.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.20",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:20",
      "text": "Fueruntque filii Juda per cognationes suas: Sela, a quo familia Selaitarum: Phares, a quo familia Pharesitarum: Zare, a quo familia Zareitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.21",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:21",
      "text": "Porro filii Phares: Hesron, a quo familia Hesronitarum: et Hamul, a quo familia Hamulitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.22",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:22",
      "text": "Istæ sunt familiæ Juda, quarum omnis numerus fuit septuaginta sex millia quingenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.23",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:23",
      "text": "Filii Issachar per cognationes suas: Thola, a quo familia Tholaitarum: Phua, a quo familia Phuaitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.24",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:24",
      "text": "Jasub, a quo familia Jasubitarum: Semran, a quo familia Semranitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.25",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:25",
      "text": "Hæ sunt cognationes Issachar, quarum numerus fuit sexaginta quatuor millia trecenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.26",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:26",
      "text": "Filii Zabulon per cognationes suas: Sared, a quo familia Sareditarum: Elon, a quo familia Elonitarum: Jalel, a quo familia Jalelitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.27",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:27",
      "text": "Hæ sunt cognationes Zabulon, quarum numerus fuit sexaginta millia quingenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.28",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:28",
      "text": "Filii Joseph per cognationes suas, Manasse et Ephraim.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.29",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:29",
      "text": "De Manasse ortus est Machir, a quo familia Machiritarum. Machir genuit Galaad, a quo familia Galaaditarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.30",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:30",
      "text": "Galaad habuit filios: Jezer, a quo familia Jezeritarum: et Helec, a quo familia Helecitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.31",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:31",
      "text": "et Asriel, a quo familia Asrielitarum: et Sechem, a quo familia Sechemitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.32",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 32,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:32",
      "text": "et Semida, a quo familia Semidaitarum: et Hepher, a quo familia Hepheritarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.33",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 33,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:33",
      "text": "Fuit autem Hepher pater Salphaad, qui filios non habebat, sed tantum filias: quarum ista sunt nomina: Maala, et Noa, et Hegla, et Melcha, et Thersa.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.34",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 34,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:34",
      "text": "Hæ sunt familiæ Manasse, et numerus earum quinquaginta duo millia septingenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.35",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 35,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:35",
      "text": "Filii autem Ephraim per cognationes suas fuerunt hi: Suthala, a quo familia Suthalaitarum: Becher, a quo familia Becheritarum: Thehen, a quo familia Thehenitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.36",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 36,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:36",
      "text": "Porro filius Suthala fuit Heran, a quo familia Heranitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.37",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 37,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:37",
      "text": "Hæ sunt cognationes filiorum Ephraim: quarum numerus fuit triginta duo millia quingenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.38",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 38,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:38",
      "text": "Isti sunt filii Joseph per familias suas. Filii Benjamin in cognationibus suis: Bela, a quo familia Belaitarum: Asbel, a quo familia Asbelitarum: Ahiram, a quo familia Ahiramitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.39",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 39,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:39",
      "text": "Supham, a quo familia Suphamitarum: Hupham, a quo familia Huphamitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.40",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 40,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:40",
      "text": "Filii Bela: Hered, et Noëman. De Hered, familia Hereditarum: de Noëman, familia Noëmanitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.41",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 41,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:41",
      "text": "Hi sunt filii Benjamin per cognationes suas: quorum numerus fuit quadraginta quinque millia sexcenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.42",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 42,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:42",
      "text": "Filii Dan per cognationes suas: Suham, a quo familia Suhamitarum. Hæ sunt cognationes Dan per familias suas.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.43",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 43,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:43",
      "text": "Omnes fuere Suhamitæ, quorum numerus erat sexaginta quatuor millia quadringenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.44",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 44,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:44",
      "text": "Filii Aser per cognationes suas: Jemna, a quo familia Jemnaitarum: Jessui, a quo familia Jessuitarum: Brie, a quo familia Brieitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.45",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 45,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:45",
      "text": "Filii Brie: Heber, a quo familia Heberitarum: et Melchiel, a quo familia Melchielitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.46",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 46,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:46",
      "text": "Nomen autem filiæ Aser fuit Sara.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.47",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 47,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:47",
      "text": "Hæ cognationes filiorum Aser, et numerus eorum quinquaginta tria millia quadringenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.48",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 48,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:48",
      "text": "Filii Nephthali per cognationes suas: Jesiel, a quo familia Jesielitarum: Guni, a quo familia Gunitarum:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.49",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 49,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:49",
      "text": "Jeser, a quo familia Jeseritarum: Sellem, a quo familia Sellemitarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.50",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 50,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:50",
      "text": "Hæ sunt cognationes filiorum Nephthali per familias suas: quorum numerus quadraginta quinque millia quadringenti.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.51",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 51,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:51",
      "text": "Ista est summa filiorum Israël, qui recensiti sunt, sexcenta millia, et mille septingenti triginta.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.52",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 52,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:52",
      "text": "Locutusque est Dominus ad Moysen, dicens:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.53",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 53,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:53",
      "text": "Istis dividetur terra juxta numerum vocabulorum in possessiones suas.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.54",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 54,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:54",
      "text": "Pluribus majorem partem dabis, et paucioribus minorem: singulis, sicut nunc recensiti sunt, tradetur possessio:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.55",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 55,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:55",
      "text": "ita dumtaxat ut sors terram tribubus dividat et familiis.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.56",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 56,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:56",
      "text": "Quidquid sorte contigerit, hoc vel plures accipiant, vel pauciores.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.57",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 57,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:57",
      "text": "Hic quoque est numerus filiorum Levi per familias suas: Gerson, a quo familia Gersonitarum: Caath, a quo familia Caathitarum: Merari, a quo familia Meraritarum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.58",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 58,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:58",
      "text": "Hæ sunt familiæ Levi: familia Lobni, familia Hebroni, familia Moholi, familia Musi, familia Core. At vero Caath genuit Amram:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.59",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 59,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:59",
      "text": "qui habuit uxorem Jochabed filiam Levi, quæ nata est ei in Ægypto. Hæc genuit Amram viro suo filios, Aaron, et Moysen, et Mariam sororem eorum.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.60",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 60,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:60",
      "text": "De Aaron orti sunt Nadab et Abiu, et Eleazar et Ithamar:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.61",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 61,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:61",
      "text": "quorum Nadab et Abiu mortui sunt, cum obtulissent ignem alienum coram Domino.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.62",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 62,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:62",
      "text": "Fueruntque omnes qui numerati sunt, viginti tria millia generis masculini ab uno mense et supra: quia non sunt recensiti inter filios Israël, nec eis cum ceteris data possessio est.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.63",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 63,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:63",
      "text": "Hic est numerus filiorum Israël, qui descripti sunt a Moyse et Eleazaro sacerdote, in campestribus Moab supra Jordanem contra Jericho:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "vulgate:numbers.26.64",
      "translationId": "vulgate",
      "bookSlug": "numbers",
      "chapterNumber": 26,
      "verseNumber": 64,
      "referenceLabel": "Numbers 26:64",
